description:
in 2015, Stéphane Mercier met Kenny Garrett during the Tournai Jazz Festival (Belgium). Great to hear where he comes from...
An Avalon Production: André Bontems, Annie Theunissen, Emilie Boumal.
fulltitle: Kenny Garrett exclusive interview by Stéphane Mercier (French subtitles)
